data.description: This charming single-story home features 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The sizable living room and family room provide a comfortable space for relaxation, while the hardwood floors add a touch of elegance. The eat-in kitchen offers a convenient and practical area for meals and gatherings. Numerous upgrades delivered to provide peace of mind including most newer Anderson windows, furnace/central air, roof and gutters. Outdoors, you will appreciate the insulated detached 2 car garage, patio and delightful curb appeal. With its thoughtful layout and desirable features, this home is sure to capture your attention. Call today for your private tour before it's too late!
